Transform
public class TransformSE_EffectiveOptions extends TransformCopy
Detects options on SERVICE and materializes them. In the case of self-join-checks an optimizer will be run preemptively unless the option 'optimizer:off' is present. 
 SERVICE <loop:> {
   SERIVCE <bulk:> {
      SERVICE <https://dbpedia.org/sparql> { }
   }
 }
becomes 
 SERVICE <loop:bulk:https://dbpedia.org/sparql> { }
